OL,3,CAdam Peaty receives honorary degree at
OL,4,CLoughborough University
OL,6,FThree-time Olympic gold medallist Adam
OL,7,FPeaty has been awarded an honorary
OL,8,Fdegree from Loughborough University in
OL,9,Frecognition of his outstanding
OL,10,Fcontribution to swimming.
OL,12,FThe ceremony, held at the university
OL,13,Fcelebrated Peaty's remarkable sporting
OL,14,Fcareer that has seen him become one of
OL,15,FGreat Britain's most decorated
OL,16,Fathletes of all time.
OL,18,FAn eight-time World Champion, he is
OL,19,Fknown for redefining the breaststroke
OL,20,Fand currently holds world records in
OL,21,Fboth the 100m and 50m events.
