OL,3,CAdam Peaty receives honorary degree at
OL,4,CLoughborough University
OL,6,FThe 29-year-old, from Uttoxeter in
OL,7,FStaffordshire, also has three Olympic
OL,8,Fsilvers to his name alongside seven
OL,9,FCommonwealth Games medals ` four gold,
OL,10,Fthree silver.
OL,12,FHe has won global medals since 2014
OL,13,Fand has won medals at three different
OL,14,FOlympic Games - Rio 2016, Tokyo 2020
OL,15,Fand Paris 2024.
OL,17,FHe currently holds the fastest all-
OL,18,Ftime 100m breaststroke times, first
OL,19,Fbreaking the world record in April
OL,20,F2015, at the British Championships in
OL,21,FLondon.
