OL,3,CAdam Peaty receives honorary degree at
OL,4,CLoughborough University
OL,6,FHe is the only athlete to swim in the
OL,7,F100m breaststroke in under 57 seconds,
OL,8,Fwhich he achieved in July 2019 at the
OL,9,FWorld Championships in South Korea.
OL,11,FIn addition to his sporting success,
OL,12,FPeaty has used his platform to
OL,13,Fadvocate for mental health awareness,
OL,14,Fopenly discussing his personal
OL,15,Fstruggles and encouraging others to
OL,16,Fseek support.
