OL,3,CAdam Peaty receives honorary degree at
OL,4,CLoughborough University
OL,6,FPeaty, who has long been associated
OL,7,Fwith Loughborough as part of Aquatic
OL,8,FGB's high-performance centre based at
OL,9,Fthe university, expressed his
OL,10,Fgratitude during the ceremony:
OL,12,F"I'm extremely proud to receive this
OL,13,Fhonorary degree from Loughborough
OL,14,FUniversity," Peaty said.
