OL,3,CAdam Peaty receives honorary degree at
OL,4,CLoughborough University
OL,6,F"After spending most of my career
OL,7,Ftraining on campus, I've seen it go
OL,8,Ffrom strength to strength, and I can
OL,9,Fsee why it's one of the top
OL,10,Funiversities in the country. I'll
OL,11,Falways have so many positive memories
OL,12,Fabout my time here and I can't wait to
OL,13,Fsee the next generation come through
OL,14,Fthe pathway which they invest so
OL,15,Fheavily in."
