OL,3,CAdam Peaty receives honorary degree at
OL,4,CLoughborough University
OL,6,FProfessor Nick Jennings, Vice-
OL,7,FChancellor and President of
OL,8,FLoughborough University, presented
OL,9,FPeaty with the honorary degree,
OL,10,Fhighlighting his relentless pursuit of
OL,11,Fexcellence and role as an
OL,12,Finspirational figure in sport.
OL,14,F"Adam embodies the values we hold at
OL,15,FLoughborough: determination,
OL,16,Fdedication, and a passion for pushing
OL,17,Fboundaries," said Professor Jennings.
