OL,3,CAdam Peaty receives honorary degree at
OL,4,CLoughborough University
OL,6,F"His unrivalled dedication to his
OL,7,Fcraft and his leadership in promoting
OL,8,Fmental health awareness make him a
OL,9,Frole model not only for our students
OL,10,Fbut for aspiring athletes worldwide.
OL,12,F"By taking a stand and using his voice
OL,13,Ffor good, Adam is playing a vital role
OL,14,Fin helping eradicate stigmas and
OL,15,Fempowering communities. Not unlike his
OL,16,Fstellar performances in the pool over
OL,17,Fmany years, he's proving himself a
OL,18,Fchampion in this space too."
